 systems,
 and entities subject to the ECIO Policy Manual,
 including Information Operations personnel,
 non-IT County employees,
 appointed and elected officials,
 and contractors and vendors who access,
 administer,
 or support County information systems,
 infrastructure,
 or data governed by the Information Operations Department.
\end_layout

